## Upcoming Milestones

### Q2 2024: v1.0.0 - Production Ready
**Target Release**: March 31, 2024  
**Focus**: Stability, security, production deployment

#### Features
- [ ] Security audit completion
- [ ] Performance optimization
- [ ] Enhanced error handling
- [ ] Production deployment guides
- [ ] Multi-sig admin support
- [ ] Backup and recovery procedures

#### Goals
- Production deployment on mainnet
- Enterprise security certification
- Partner integrations

### Q2 2024: v1.1.0 - Enhanced Compliance
**Target Release**: May 31, 2024  
**Focus**: Advanced compliance features, regulatory enhancements

#### Features
- [ ] Dynamic policy engine
- [ ] Time-based restrictions
- [ ] Volume-based limits
- [ ] Enhanced reporting
- [ ] Audit trail improvements
- [ ] Custom rule engine

#### Goals
- Support for complex compliance requirements
- Regulatory compliance for major jurisdictions
- Institutional adoption

### Q3 2024: v1.2.0 - Token Extensions Maturity
**Target Release**: July 31, 2024  
**Focus**: Advanced token features, developer experience

#### Features
- [ ] Additional token extensions support
- [ ] Metadata integration
- [ ] Advanced transfer hooks
- [ ] UI component library
