### Q4 2024: v2.0.0 - Multi-chain & Advanced Features
**Target Release**: December 31, 2024  
**Focus**: Cross-chain support, advanced features

#### Features
- [ ] Cross-chain compliance
- [ ] Privacy features (ZK proofs)
